flowchart TD
    Start([Relying service needs human approval]) --> ValidateRequest[Validate relay handle, service, action, and declared risk]
    ValidateRequest -->|Invalid public input| GenericReject[Return generic request failure]
    ValidateRequest -->|Valid shape| ResolveCandidate[Resolve opaque relay handle to one active account]
    ResolveCandidate -->|Unknown, disabled, or throttled| GenericReject
    ResolveCandidate -->|Active| BuildProjection[Build PII-free model projection]

    BuildProjection --> ClassifyAction[GPT-5.6 returns typed purpose, summary, and suggested risk]
    ClassifyAction -->|Timeout, refusal, or invalid schema| ConservativeFallback[Use conservative high-risk fallback]
    ClassifyAction -->|Valid output| ClampRisk[Server computes maximum final risk]
    ConservativeFallback --> ClampRisk

    ClampRisk --> CreateRequest[Persist relay request and one-time challenge digest]
    CreateRequest --> VaultLookup[Notification boundary resolves encrypted destination]
    VaultLookup -->|Vault or delivery failure| DeliveryFailed[Record generic delivery failure]
    VaultLookup -->|Destination available| SendChallenge[Simulated SMS adapter receives plaintext destination]
    SendChallenge --> MaskDestination[Discard plaintext and return masked destination]
    MaskDestination --> AwaitCode[Account holder submits OTP outside GPT]

    AwaitCode --> VerifyState{Request active and code valid?}
    VerifyState -->|Expired, consumed, or too many attempts| GenericVerifyFailure[Return generic verification failure]
    VerifyState -->|Wrong code with attempts remaining| IncrementAttempt[Atomically increment attempt count]
    IncrementAttempt --> GenericVerifyFailure
    VerifyState -->|Valid code| ConsumeChallenge[Atomically consume challenge]
    ConsumeChallenge --> IssueReceipt[Create pseudonymous verification receipt]
    IssueReceipt --> ReturnReceipt[Return receipt without PII]
    ReturnReceipt --> Complete([Relying service receives proof of account control])

    ClassifyAction -. no tools or PII .-> ModelBoundary[Model cannot send, verify, or issue]
    VaultLookup -. only decryption boundary .-> VaultBoundary[General application never receives raw phone]
